items.badge_name: Cheers to Independent U.S. Craft Breweries (Level 17)
items.badge_description: Cheers, beer patriot! You are supporting the small and independent American craft brewer. When you see the seal -- shaped like an upside-down beer bottle -- that's independence you're tasting. Try 5 more to earn Level 18!

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 100 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 21!

Canning is all the rage and it's not hard to see why - travels well, more environmentally friendly, and no need to carry your bottle opener. That's 65 checkins with the serving style of Can. Try 5 more for Level 14!

user.bio:
I ain't drunk, I'm just drinkin'
- Albert Collins

items.badge_description: Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 310 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower.
Keep the party rolling all day long with your favorite low ABV session IPAs. That's 10 different beers with style of IPA - Session / India Session Ale. Try 5 more for Level 3!
We believe in IPA and you should too. You certainly have a taste for the hops! That's 70 different IPAs. Try 5 more for Level 15!

user.location: I come from the land of ice and snow.

user.bio: Travel for both business and pleasure. Very fortunate to have had some amazing beers around the world.

items.badge_description: It takes the perfect amount of light, the right framing and a touch of creative love to get the perfect picture of your brew. Now it’s time to drink it! That’s 20 check-ins with a photo.

You’ve pledged allegiance, and now it’s time to enjoy some beer! Now remember, not all American beer is fizzy and yellow. That’s 20 different beers from a brewery in the United States. Try 5 more for Level 5.

Fresh from the tap is one of the best ways to enjoy a beer. Just try to use a glass and not drink directly from the tap, as tempting as it may be. That's 135 checkins with the serving style of Draft. Try 5 more for Level 28!
Keep the party rolling all day long with your favorite low ABV session IPAs. That's 10 different beers with style of IPA - Session / India Session Ale. Try 5 more for Level 3!

items.checkin_comment: For an IPA, it pretty good. Not too overtly hoppy.
